!Sample_extract_protocol_ch1 = Cell suspensions were then washed, counted, pooled, concentrated, and subjected to 5â² single-cell RNA sequencing using the Chromium Next GEM Single Cell 5â² Kit v2 and Chromium Next GEM Chip K Single Cell Kit (10x Genomics, Pleasanton, CA, USA), targeting a recovery of 10,000 cells using manufacturerâs protocols. Sequencing libraries were prepared using the Library Construction Kit (10x Genomics, Pleasanton, CA, USA) and sequenced on an Illumina NextSeq 2000. Cells were stained using TotalSeq-C hashtag and CITE-Seq antibodies. Cell suspensions were then washed, counted, pooled, concentrated, and subjected to 5â² single-cell RNA sequencing using the Chromium Next GEM Single Cell 5â² Kit v2 and Chromium Next GEM Chip K Single Cell Kit, targeting a recovery of 10,000 cells.
